            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="mb-3">Visa Options for Job Seekers in UAE</h4>

                    <h5 class="text-primary">1. UAE Job Seeker Visa</h5>
                    <p>This visa allows job seekers to enter the UAE without a job offer to explore opportunities.</p>
                      <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Valid for 60, 90, or 120 days</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Requires Bachelor's degree</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>No sponsor required</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Apply via 
                        <a href="https://icp.gov.ae/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ICP Smart Services</a> 
                        or 
                        <a href="https://www.gdrfad.gov.ae/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GDRFA Dubai</a>
                    </li>
                    </ul>


                    <h5 class="text-primary mt-4">2. Visit Visa (Tourist Visa for Job Hunt)</h5>
                    <p>Used by many to visit UAE and explore job opportunities.</p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Valid for 30 or 60 days</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Sponsor usually required</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Can convert to work visa after job offer</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h5 class="text-primary mt-4">3. Golden Visa</h5>
                    <p>A long-term residency option for skilled professionals, investors, and talent.</p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Valid for 5 to 10 years</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Salary requirement: AED 30,000+</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>No employer sponsorship needed</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h5 class="text-primary mt-4">4. Green Visa</h5>
                    <p>Targeted at freelancers, skilled employees, and self-employed individuals.</p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Valid for 5 years</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Requires bachelor's degree or diploma</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Salary threshold: AED 15,000+</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Freelance permit required from MOHRE</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h5 class="text-primary mt-4">Important Tips</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><i class="fa fa-info-circle text-primary me-2"></i>Always use government portals or trusted consultants.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-info-circle text-primary me-2"></i>Do not overstay your visa to avoid penalties or bans.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-info-circle text-primary me-2"></i>You may search and attend interviews while on a tourist/visit visa.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-info-circle text-danger me-2"></i>Working on a tourist visa is illegal and can result in fines, bans, or deportation.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-info-circle text-primary me-2"></i>Convert to a valid work visa before joining any job.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-info-circle text-primary me-2"></i>Refer to 
                            <a href="https://icp.gov.ae/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ICP Smart Services</a> or 
                            <a href="https://www.gdrfad.gov.ae/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GDRFA</a> for updates.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

